{"tid":1528981,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"戇鳩藍絲愚民唔知基本法授予集會自由，不如每次集會背景都舉BANNER","createTime":"2019-09-01T15:45:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T00:04:31.000Z","uid":92479,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"93db7be8e6aef5da06976a5eb38bcaced362ffd9","tid":1528981,"uid":92479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T15:45:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">用基本法屌柒公安條例，今次要比記者做集會焦點</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/gangtai/xl1-03302015103013.html/80547f7258f0660e8868793a-5e9463097167300a57fa672c6cd5300b7b2c276761768489c45b9a4fdd62a45b66672f81ea7531.JPG/@@images/75974468-166a-4ce5-a888-14bddfcd8b3c.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fmandarin%2Fyataibaodao%2Fgangtai%2Fxl1-03302015103013.html%2F80547f7258f0660e8868793a-5e9463097167300a57fa672c6cd5300b7b2c276761768489c45b9a4fdd62a45b66672f81ea7531.JPG%2F%40%40images%2F75974468-166a-4ce5-a888-14bddfcd8b3c.jpeg&h=646ff233&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><br />\n根據基本法第27條規定「香港居民享有言論、新聞、出版的自由，結社、集會、遊行、示威的自由，組織和參加工會、罷工的權利和自由。」 ... 除了基本法，《香港人權法案條例》第5條也訂明「人人有權享有身體自由及人身安全，任何人不得無理予以逮捕或拘禁」</span>"},{"pid":"ba2dd725ea7cb9469de6a92db41a328ed9c54a63","tid":1528981,"uid":92479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T15:46:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ece6dfcadc12cce0ad2a19efa532838f3bd1f9c4","tid":1528981,"uid":259345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T15:47:10.000Z","msg":"我忍左佢好撚耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一句講晒 聽日麻包袋藍絲副校長 割唔割<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1528684\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1528684</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a984f409dc0847f33e49adc592fd553e1d8598fd","tid":1528981,"uid":94978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T15:48:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da75f7eab9a7fd99245fe812f920acab43de82ff","tid":1528981,"uid":92479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T16:04:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ecc9be676b2b4304b36f2db2d013399f687106c","tid":1528981,"uid":92479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T16:05:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1565e508ceda490e2c11462f4a886c12d7a6d89d","tid":1528981,"uid":19178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T16:05:42.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"343f95c45bf14210fcde97c172e028a73a7d0973","tid":1528981,"uid":257422,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T16:05:52.000Z","msg":"支持，不過藍絲無腦有時真係無得救<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/09/01/223606_db1fcc72048388792c25c8bdc081a00b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F09%2F01%2F223606_db1fcc72048388792c25c8bdc081a00b.gif&h=16fdca9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">全民學唱<span style=\"color: red;\">美國</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">國歌</span><br />\n</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1528828\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1528828</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大家仲記唔記得手足揮美國國旗唱美國國歌唱到Trump Trump都retweet!!!!</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><